  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For the linear function&nbsp;<math alttext=\"f\"><mi>f</mi></math>, the graph of&nbsp;<math alttext=\"y equals f left parenthesis x right parenthesis\"><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>f</mi><mfenced><mi>x</mi></mfenced></math> in the <em>xy</em>-plane has a slope of&nbsp;<math alttext=\"one fourth\"><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac></math> and passes through the point&nbsp;<math alttext=\"left parenthesis 0 comma 5 right parenthesis\"><mfenced><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>5</mn></mrow></mfenced></math>. Which equation defines&nbsp;<math alttext=\"f\"><mi>f</mi></math>?</p>",
