      "content": "<p><math alttext=\"f left parenthesis x right parenthesis equals one fourth x plus 5\"><mi>f</mi><mfenced><mi>x</mi></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><mn>4</mn></mrow></mfrac><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mrow><mn>5</mn></mrow></math></p>"
